_sText:
3 Floor Building (4 Including basement)
12+12 variable spawn points
Basement connecting with outside of mansion boundaries using a tunnel.
You can access outside boundaries from rooftop jumping down on a ledge and get back in using the tunnel
Breakable glass windows which can be shot through and also shoot-break at spots
Various hidden points and sniper spots

Bot Navigation file included
Custom textures included
Optimized visportals for better framerate

I had to remove some artifacts in release version because they were creating very low frame-rate on 20+ players multiplayer.

Match suitable for deathmatch and gungame
